# Test Results Directory

Test results will be saved here automatically when running performance tests.

## Files Generated

- `frontend-metrics-{timestamp}.json` - Frontend performance metrics (bundle size, build time)
- `backend-metrics-{timestamp}.json` - Backend API performance metrics (response times)
- `k6-results-{timestamp}.json` - Load testing results from k6
- `performance-report-{timestamp}.md` - Formatted report summary

## Usage

Run tests from parent directory:
```powershell
cd ..
.\run-all-tests.ps1 -All
```

Parse and view results:
```powershell
.\parse-results.ps1
```
